>> title: Ginger Drop
>> tags: whiskey,tumbler,rolled,ginger

Fill a #tumbler{} with @ice{} (either a rock or a few large cubes).

Add @rye whiskey{1.5%oz}, @Domaine de Canton ginger liqueur{1/2%oz}, and @lemon juice{1/2%oz}.

Roll ingredients gently in glass (or gently stir with barspoon).

Garnish with @lemon twist{1}.